And the best overall response rates, as you can see, were 50 percent higher than what we have observed.

00:03:52.880 --> 00:03:58.880
So, in conclusion, this trial shows that fixed duration, fixed treatment duration of long-coxytuximab

00:03:58.880 --> 00:04:05.120
rituximab showed no new safety signals and it has promising activity. We are, however, awaiting

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:11.600
the randomization studies for definitive results. Now, moving on to the LOTYS7,

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:16.480
which was essentially a combination of long-coxytuximab to serine with the glofitamab.

00:04:16.480 --> 00:04:21.920
This study started out with the 3+3 design. Long-coxytuximab was tested in

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:29.120
90, 120, and 150 micrograms per kilogram. And then the study was moved on to the phase 2 portion

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:36.160
in the dose expansion arm, where long-coxytuximab was tested in 120 or 150 micrograms per kilogram

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:41.920
in combination of glofitamab. This was also finite duration treatment. Long-coxytuximab was given for

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:49.920
8 cycles and glofitamab was given for 12 cycles. During cycle 1 day 1, obinutuzumab pre-treatment

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:56.640
was given cycle 1 day 2. Long-coxytuximab was given and glofitamab was started on day 8 of cycle 1.

00:04:56.640 --> 00:05:02.320
And subsequently, both long-coxytuximab and glofitamab were given every 3 weeks.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:12.560
This is the study population. Total of 49 patients were enrolled. The median age was 70 years in

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:19.760
both groups. Majority of patients had de novo DLBCL. Half of the patients had germinal center cell of

00:05:19.760 --> 00:05:29.280
origin. And 16% of patients had double and triple hit as a subtype of DLBCL lymphoma. Median prior

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:38.240
line subtherapies were 1. And prior CAR-T cell therapy was in 16% of patients. And primary

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:44.240
refractory disease was present in half of the patients. In general, this is a busy table,

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:49.600
but essentially, grade 3, 4 treatment-related adverse events,

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:55.920
the event rate was 80%. And grade 5 or serious adverse event rate was also similar to what we

00:05:55.920 --> 00:06:02.080
normally observe with long-coxytuximab. The point of showing this table is essentially the combination

00:06:02.080 --> 00:06:06.960
of long-coxytuximab and glofitamab did not have any additive toxicity. And the side effects were

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:13.120
pretty much what we expect from the single agents. Now, in terms of cytokine release syndrome, you can

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:19.440
see here the CRS rate was considerably lower, almost half in patients who received 150 microgram

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:25.120
per kilogram compared to 120 microgram per kilogram. Majority of the CRS were limited to

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:31.200
grade 1 and 2. Only one patient developed grade 3 CRS. ICANS rate was also quite low. Only two

00:06:31.200 --> 00:06:37.040
patients in the 120 microgram per kilogram developed ICANS. There were no ICANS in the

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:43.040
higher dose of long-coxytuximab . Based on this data, the 150 microgram

00:06:43.040 --> 00:06:49.280
per kilogram dose is being moved forward for more patient enrollment. The dose discontinuation

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:54.880
of both long-coxytuximab, tesirine, and glofitamab was also extremely low, around 6% or so.

00:06:56.160 --> 00:07:01.200
Now, the efficacy data is something I want to highlight here. The overall response rates are

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:07.680
90%, quite high in both groups. And the complete response rate are approximately 78%.

00:07:08.320 --> 00:07:13.280
In relapsed DL-BCL setting, these complete response rates are considered quite promising.

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:19.120
And the median time to CR and time to response was approximately six weeks. That's when the

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:25.280
first scans were performed. So, in conclusion, long-coxytuximab and glofitamab has demonstrated

00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:31.840
promising activity with an overall response rate of 81.9% and complete response rate of 77%

00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:40.000
in relapsed large B-cell lymphoma. CRS of all grades was 25% as selected 150 microgram per

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:48.960
kilogram dose and 52% at 120 microgram per kilogram dose. And ICANS rates was 4.1% across

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:56.160
dose levels and all were grade one and two. Thank you so much.
